---
title: Spicy Buffalo Cauliflower Flatbreads with Mozzarella, Scallions, Carrot Sticks & Ranch Dressing
description: Spicy, tangy Buffalo sauce brings huge flavor to anything it touches! To make these cheesy, crispy flatbreads, you’ll toss tender roasted florets in Buffalo sauce and pile them onto flatbreads along with a shower of easy-melting mozzarella. Hot enough for you? Carrot sticks and creamy buttermilk ranch dressing cool things down.
